text: Muriel Marland-Militello (30 July 1943 – 25 February 2021) was a French politician. She was a member of the National Assembly of France from 2002 to 2012. Marland-Militello was born in Nice, France. Marland-Militello died on 25 February 2021 in Nice, aged 77.Nice : décès de l'ancienne adjointe et députée niçoise Muriel Marland-Militello ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Politicians from Nice
